 <PERSON> Robert </PERSON> <PERSON> H. </PERSON> <PERSON> Reid </PERSON> is chief of the <ORGANIZATION> AP </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> bureau </ORGANIZATION> in <LOCATION> Manila </LOCATION>.
